    "title": "Junior SEO Specialist at Spencer's Retail",
    "description": "Spencer's Retail invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of SEO Specialist at our Nagpur location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Spencer's Retail:\nSpencer's Retail is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nagpur, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Spencer's Retail!",
